OL,3,CEd Davey calls for return of 'family
OL,4,Cdoctor' by giving over-70s named GP
OL,6,FThe Lib Dems are also campaigning for
OL,7,F8,000 more GPs to be recruited in
OL,8,Fresponse to a "crisis" in general
OL,9,Fpractice waiting times.
OL,11,FSir Ed said: "Years of neglect and
OL,12,Fbroken promises under this
OL,13,FConservative government have left
OL,14,Fpeople struggling to see their local
OL,15,FGP when they need to. It is piling
OL,16,Fpressure on to overcrowded hospitals
OL,17,Fand meaning patients with easily
OL,18,Fpreventable and treatable conditions
OL,19,Faren't getting the rapid care they
OL,20,Fneed.
