OL,3,CEd Davey calls for return of 'family
OL,4,Cdoctor' by giving over-70s named GP
OL,6,F"We want to see the return of the
OL,7,Ffamily doctor, so patients with long-
OL,8,Fterm care needs see the same GP and
OL,9,Fdon't have to waste time repeating
OL,10,Ftheir details from scratch at every
OL,11,Fappointment.
OL,13,F"This would provide vital personalised
OL,14,Fcare for those who need it most,
OL,15,Fhelping people lead healthier lives,
OL,16,Findependently in their own homes
OL,17,Fwherever possible."
